 missing dependency: 'socketRef'. Either include it or remove the dependency array. Mutable values like 'socketRef.current' aren't valid dependencies because mutating them doesn't re-render the component.",["75"],["76"],{"desc":"77","fix":"78"},{"desc":"79","fix":"80"},{"desc":"81","fix":"82"},{"desc":"77","fix":"83"},"Update the dependencies array to be: [location.state?.username, reactNavigator, roomId]",{"range":"84","text":"85"},"Update the dependencies array to be: [onCodeChange, roomId, socketRef]",{"range":"86","text":"87"},"Update the dependencies array to be: [socketRef]",{"range":"88","text":"89"},{"range":"90","text":"85"},[2563,2565],"[location.state?.username, reactNavigator, roomId]",[1323,1325],"[onCodeChange, roomId, socketRef]",[1687,1706],"[socketRef]",[2563,2565]]